{"title":"葬瘟神","authors":["易和元"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":1,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"葬瘟神"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"易和元"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古巴圣地亚哥城的群众为艾森豪威尔下台举行象征性的埋葬游行。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一支支蜡烛手中擎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一辆灵车后面跟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古巴人民把歌唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢天喜地葬瘟神！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诅咒你，这瘟神，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"埋葬你，这瘟神，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"罪恶滔天万人恨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"散布瘟疫害人民。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古巴人民闹翻身，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你满肚子不高兴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张牙舞爪恶狠狠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要充当国际宪兵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"实行经济封锁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出动海陆空军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"策动武装叛乱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在加勒比海挑衅！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十八般解数你都使出，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一计未成，二计又生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你这瘟神，你这害人精，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一心要扼杀古巴人民！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"针锋相对，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚持斗争，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利的是古巴人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倒霉的是你这瘟神！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一支支蜡烛手中擎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一辆灵车后面跟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古巴人民把歌唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢天喜地葬瘟神！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"加勒比海波涛滚滚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌颂古巴人民的斗争；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"加勒比海波涛滚滚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"埋葬你这万恶的瘟神！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}